{"tid":2069004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日下午四點 台灣陸委會開記者會 解說‘香港人道援助關懷專案’！","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T07:13:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a57f2ee2902908c436f1319c006b6a9ee2e4ed27","tid":2069004,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:47:22.000Z","msg":"陸委會下午4時就「香港人道援助關懷行動專案」舉行記者會，由主委陳明通主持。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會早前表示，總統蔡英文對於港人的關懷不變，依指示所作的相關方案規劃，對於國內相關民間團體長期關注香港民主自由人權，並展現力挺香港、守護台灣的決心，表達敬佩與尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2497722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2497722&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=987bd95e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2497722</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但都應咗老燒推斷<br />\n全世界趕住接收港人<br />\n即係國安法過硬，仲大大鑊"},{"pid":"e222369339eba201e2d2700f820f4216f1b24746","tid":2069004,"uid":153151,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e1b2c254b3336ef272acb8e6f5607c4e6622d591","tid":2069004,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2068899/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2068899/page/1</a><br />\n[內附懶人包]一鍵投訴紅官蘇文隆<br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"ad9656ede8e50157451e7573587a50a710856f9e","tid":2069004,"uid"